normal mode:
hjkl --move
esc --return to normal mode
u --undo
x --delete char
dd --delete line
r --replace char
+p --paste
. --repeat operation
$ --goto end


Edit modes:
i --insert
I --insert in beginning
a --append
A --append at the end

command mode:
: --enter command mode
w --save
q --quit
q! --force quit
wq --save and quit
set number --numbering lines
! --run command

visual mode:
v --character-wise visual mode
V --line-wise visual mode
ctrl-v --line-wise visual mode
u --lowercase
U --uppercase
d --delete
c --change
y --yank
> --indent
< --dedent


my settings:
shift-f2 --vs code toggle vim extension